- Steps display progress through a sequence of logical and numbered steps. They may also be used for navigation.

### Default

```jsx
  <Steps steps={steps5} activeStepIndex={2} />
```

### No navigation buttons

```jsx
<Steps
    steps={steps5}
    activeStepIndex={2}
    areNavigationButtonsHidden
    className="monday-storybook-steps_padding"
  />
```

### With number indicator
```jsx
<Flex direction="column" gap="medium">
  <Steps type="numbers" steps={steps5} activeStepIndex={2} />
</Flex>
```